text: Gong Chan-sik (born August 14, 1993), also known as Gongchan, is a South Korean singer and actor. He is a member of the South Korean boy group B1A4, formed under the label WM Entertainment. == Personal life == Gongchan was confirmed by WM to be exempted from mandatory military service due to health reasons. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1993 births Category:B1A4 members Category:Living people Category:Pop singers Category:South Korean television actors Category:Stage names
